import React from 'react'
import { Navbar , Home , Contact, Signup , Login,  About } from './components'
import { Route,Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
    
    <Navbar/>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Home/>
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/contact">
        <Contact/>
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/about">
        <Home/>
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Home/>
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Home/>
      </Route>
    </Switch>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
